{"tid":683233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉警署內盜疑被捕女子約3000元　一警周三提堂一警無條件釋放","createTime":"2018-05-29T13:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T14:25:28.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04c09a11a33c989b97c698c7aa6ace66f7e1ea1c","tid":683233,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">涉警署內盜疑被捕女子約3000元　一警周三提堂一警無條件釋放</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n警方星期二（29日）晚公布，4月12日下午4時20分接報，兩名年齡分別是31歲及32歲的警務人員，在柴灣分區執行任務。其間一名34歲女子，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」被捕，並被帶返柴灣警署。該女子其後發現，有約3000元現金失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警方人員其後主動調查，發現該兩名警務人員涉嫌盜竊，拘捕及扣留兩人調查，交港島總區重案組跟進。兩人其後都獲准保釋候查，本月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，控告32歲警務人員一項盜竊罪，星期三（30日）東區裁判法院提堂。另一名31歲警務人員，則獲無條件釋放。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180529/s00001/1527602069061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2F1527602069061&d=3bx6tFPt1d4aR3eCtR1RLAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fae1114a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2F1527602069061&h=6036a380\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180529/s00001/1527602069061</a><br />\n<br />\n值班警+1"},{"pid":"4c3e8a49dec6a8a8589f04fb1b4bf750e58887ea","tid":683233,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c09a11a33c989b97c698c7aa6ace66f7e1ea1c","tid":683233,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">涉警署內盜疑被捕女子約3000元　一警周三提堂一警無條件釋放</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n警方星期二（29日）晚公布，4月12日下午4時20分接報，兩名年齡分別是31歲及32歲的警務人員，在柴灣分區執行任務。其間一名34歲女子，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」被捕，並被帶返柴灣警署。該女子其後發現，有約3000元現金失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警方人員其後主動調查，發現該兩名警務人員涉嫌盜竊，拘捕及扣留兩人調查，交港島總區重案組跟進。兩人其後都獲准保釋候查，本月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，控告32歲警務人員一項盜竊罪，星期三（30日）東區裁判法院提堂。另一名31歲警務人員，則獲無條件釋放。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180529/s00001/1527602069061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2F1527602069061&d=3bx6tFPt1d4aR3eCtR1RLAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=fae1114a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180529%2Fs00001%2F1527602069061&h=6036a380\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180529/s00001/1527602069061</a><br />\n<br />\n值班警+1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:01:21.000Z","msg":"只係3000元............."},{"pid":"4969ab43bf8f8e58d9177296fb538dcea2fd4d30","tid":683233,"uid":15658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母個標題睇撚左4 ,5 次先明佢up 乜<br />\n依家d 報紙佬係咪唔撚識字"},{"pid":"5a62f870919a3a35bb5486772e1dc20f0d36cd8e","tid":683233,"uid":95,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"之前有單係掃黃嗰時偷鳳姐幾千蚊皮肉錢，勁仆街"},{"pid":"e87d905629a334ef45801682db0a65ba70dd7987","tid":683233,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"兩萬幾都偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196578e799846d87b88689d96618afb1fe956d8a","tid":683233,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af9e2df46a23719ec2fd6fb4f60989a69efcdee","tid":683233,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"人哋離鄉別井做雞。依家被佢拉完，連皮肉錢都要偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢樣當更警值得 +10啦<img src=\"/assets/